cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.SD 

This paper discusses the design and evaluation of emotionally expressive storytelling agents, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and affective computing (cs.SD). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.HC and cs.RO, followed by cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.SD.
